Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(463.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:23.76,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(495.495,236.833)}The Monstrous Cobra Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Put those fangs into your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When Substance A,\Nintegrated into those fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,combines with Substance\NB from your ears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and is forced out by\Nthe pump in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it will allowing you to\Ndissolve any substance at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me! Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is no longer\Nuseful as a combatant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll make a perfect\Ntest subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We will use Cobra Man's powers to\Nacquire all of the world's gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We will start with the\NJapanese gold repository,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then move onto\NAmerica, then England,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then the gold repositories of\Nevery country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Cobra Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Japanese gold repository!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:44.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\3c&H493416&\c&H73919B&\bord4}Ministry of Finance\NGold Repository
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! It's just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Kondo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for a shift\Nchange, Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NI'll leave it in your hands, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing out of the\Nordinary in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take off early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get home as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your boy is lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when he's with our dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't care what\Nhis old man does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone... come help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he needs to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This gold will all\Nbelong to Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.02,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\bord2\fs60}Gold Reserves Attacked Last Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.02,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\bord2\fs60}No Gold Bars Taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.10,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\bord2\fs60}Investigation Regarding \NDeath of Security Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.19,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Shocker must be behind\Nthis latest incident, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.59,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,What could they be after?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're targeting gold\Nin various countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be trying to\Ntake over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruri, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, coffee please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Are you going\Nto the gold reserve, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch Shocker's\Ntrail this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a charm of\Nprotection in the locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bell for the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we never know\Nwhere you might run off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your dog\Nbrought my fangs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fangs? I don't...\Nknow what you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that. Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And what did you do\Nwith its corpse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:58.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H98C5E0&\c&H562B15&}Here Lies Dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're in heaven\Nnow, Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:59.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the child!\NHe's done nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We require the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:13.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's ears can hear sounds up\Nto four kilometers in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:19.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He could tell exactly which direction\Nthe underground Cobra Man was moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:31.40,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,530)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One kilometer west-southwest.\NI'm almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the fangs are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body will burn just like\Nthat when it touches that fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,\Ntell me where the fangs are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a moth to a flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've planted mines\Nall around the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man! Return the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one step closer,\NKamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, or the child dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the child's life\Nmean nothing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender now, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands up! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That Takeshi really knows\Nhow to worry a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is it, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the cat's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:36.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the Kamen Rider had\Nfallen into Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:41.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He'd been brought to Shocker's laboratory\Nto complete his Shocker brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the surgery is finished, you'll\Nbecome a cyborg acting at my beck and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And once that's done, there will\Nbe no one left to stand against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Takehiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran the child through a lie detector, and\Nhe really doesn't know where the fangs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take six more months\Nto create new fangs for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You will need to\Nwait until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But without those fangs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I destroyed those fangs and\Nthrew them in the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find them, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now escape, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch over him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man...\NI can't let you go after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider beat the\Nguy who killed Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Kamen Rider going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.93,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H98C5E0&\c&H562B15&}Here Lies Dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So Cobra Man's fangs were\Nhere the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, miss! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I wonder who came\Nto visit Dummy's grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could see\Nthe Kamen Rider again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I have\Nto go to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the Kamen Rider\Nto meet you some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...\Nbut you'd better not be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why Takeshi\Ndidn't come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly where Takeshi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I put a transmitter into the\Ngood luck charm you gave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a receiver?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bell for the\Ncat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:30.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so the Kamen Rider, Hongo\NTakeshi, foiled Cobra Man's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:35.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But his rage, hatred, and determination\Nto fight Shocker only grew stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:39.88,Cont,,570,0,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,490)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:43.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:43.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next monster sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the revived Cobra Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:48.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having failed to steal\Nthe gold reserves,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker brings Cobra\NMan back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:54.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider fights to keep the\Ngold safe from Cobra Man's ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:57.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.17,0:24:00.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Reborn Cobra Man"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:10.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:12.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:14.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:17.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:20.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:21.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:25.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:27.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.57,0:24:33.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.24,0:24:36.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.83,0:24:40.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:44.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!